I walk inside and we sit down next to each other on the white, leather couch. She starts asking me questions about my ex-girlfriend at college, when I notice my step-moms legs are starting to spread. Youre not wearing any panties! I gasp. I grab her leg and help her legs spread wide open. Then, I notice that she is bald down there! She doesnt have a bush! And I suddenly notice that she isnt wearing a bra either! My step-mom unbuckled my belt, telling me that she wants to unwrap her present now.
